You can use PubMed website to reach to the List of All Journals Cited in PubMed.

The link “Pubmed journal list” directs you to the .txt file. You can download/save it.
or you can directly (by using read_tsv()) download the file from ftp link.


Original version (txt file)

Here is the example how it looks in PubMed website. The dataset actually has 278520 rows with one column (>8 mb).


Corrected format

This is an example how it looks.
